Posts.Content: This literally turned up over night. It's the size half of grain of rice and very close to the skin.
Posts.Title: Change in breast

Posts.Content: I have been trying to loose some weight and been exercising quite a bit. One day after doing arm exercises I noticed my right breast at the top had changed. When I felt it I felt a small lump near the surface that wasn't there the day before. There is a small red spot on it. It has be come smaller over time and the skin is fading, but it is still there. Could exercise have done this?
